reviews.review_msg: One of the best professors I have ever taken at SFU! Coleman genuinely cares about her students inside and outside of the classroom and is always willing to accommodate if you reach out. If you have the chance to take a class with her (especially an upper level) do it!!!

Prof. Nye is one of the most caring professors I have ever had. The class was welcoming, and it was so clear she cares for students' wellbeing. The content was more than interesting and readings were carefully chosen.
